data.description: Seller will pay $8000 towards buyer's closing costs.  Beautiful craftsman style home with 3 bedrooms PLUS an office and a huge bonus space! Open living/dining/kitchen area with lots of natural light. Kitchen features lovely wood cabinets, quarts countertops, stainless appliances, large island, and a huge walk-in pantry. Conveniently located room off the great room could serve as an office, nursery, or guest room. Upstairs is a huge space perfect for guest room, extra living room, rec room, homeschool area, and/or storage.  Outdoor living offers almost half an acre starting with a covered front porch and expansive covered back porch, extended deck with gazebo, above-ground pool, extra storage building, privacy-fenced backyard, and lots of flat grassy area for playing or gardening. Metal roof! Great neighborhood with easy access to eastside and northside shopping and activities.
